    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is offset by the direct equivalency of the single ASTM F1717 test configuration to the COU, the multi-laboratory replication across two independent test sites, and the conservative acceptance bounds applied to all QoIs. Overall credibility is sufficient to support a Medium assurance level determination for this Class II device submission.",
